== Events == * [[暦仁]] 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|1238|ja|1238}} {{ill|December 30|ja|12月30日}}） – Due to extraordinary omens, the era name was changed from {{ill|嘉禎|ja|嘉禎}} to {{ill|暦仁|ja|暦仁}}.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://example.com|title=Reference needed|accessdate=2021-04}}</ref> * [[Genroku]] 16th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1703|ja|1703}} {{ill|December 31|ja|12月31日}}） – The Genroku Great Earthquake occurred. * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1707|ja|1707}} {{ill|December 16|ja|12月16日}}) – Mount Fuji’s great eruption (the Hōei eruption) occurred; a new volcanic cone appeared on its eastern flank and was named {{ill|Hōei-yama|ja|宝永山}}. * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1853|ja|1853}} {{ill|December 23|ja|12月23日}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ietsuna|ja|徳川家定}}, the 13th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate, assumed office.
== Births == * [[寛正]] 6th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|1465|ja|1465}} {{ill|December 11|ja|12月11日}}) – {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshinobu|ja|足利義尚}}, the 9th shōgun of the Ashikaga Shogunate (died {{ill|1489|ja|1489}}).<ref>{{Kotobank|足利義尚}}</ref>
