== Events ==
* [[暦仁]] 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|1238|ja|1238}} {{ill|December 30|ja|12月30日}}） – Due to extraordinary omens, the era name was changed from {{ill|嘉禎|ja|嘉禎}} to {{ill|暦仁|ja|暦仁}}.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://example.com|title=Reference needed|accessdate=2021-04}}</ref>
