qq-November 23 (Lunisolar)-qq {{Lunisolar November|qq=}} '''November 23''' is the 23rd day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|qq=}}, the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|qq=}}.
== Events == * [[暦仁]] 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1238|ja|1238|qq=}} {{ill|December 30|ja|12月30日|qq=}}） – Due to extraordinary omens, the era name was changed from {{ill|嘉禎|ja|嘉禎|qq=}} to {{ill|暦仁|ja|暦仁|qq=}}.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://example.com|title=Reference needed|accessdate=2021-04|qq=}}</ref> * [[Genroku]] 16th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1703|ja|1703|qq=}} {{ill|December 31|ja|12月31日|qq=}}） – The Genroku Great Earthquake occurred. * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1707|ja|1707|qq=}} {{ill|December 16|ja|12月16日|qq=}}) – Mount Fuji’s great eruption (the Hōei eruption) occurred; a new volcanic cone appeared on its eastern flank and was named {{ill|Hōei-yama|ja|宝永山|qq=}}. * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1853|ja|1853|qq=}} {{ill|December 23|ja|12月23日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ietsuna|ja|徳川家定|qq=}}, the 13th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate, assumed office.
== Births == * [[寛正]] 6th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1465|ja|1465|qq=}} {{ill|December 11|ja|12月11日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshinobu|ja|足利義尚|qq=}}, the 9th shōgun of the Ashikaga Shogunate (died {{ill|1489|ja|1489|qq=}}).<ref>{{Kotobank|足利義尚|qq=}}</ref>
