* [[暦仁]] 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1238|ja|1238|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 30|ja|12月30日|qq=|12=draft}}） – Due to extraordinary omens, the era name was changed from {{ill|嘉禎|ja|嘉禎|qq=|12=draft}} to {{ill|暦仁|ja|暦仁|qq=|12=draft}}.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://example.com|title=Reference needed|accessdate=2021-04|qq=}}</ref>
* [[Genroku]] 16th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1703|ja|1703|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 31|ja|12月31日|qq=|12=draft}}） – The Genroku Great Earthquake occurred.
* {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1707|ja|1707|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 16|ja|12月16日|qq=|12=draft}}) – Mount Fuji’s great eruption (the Hōei eruption) occurred; a new volcanic cone appeared on its eastern flank and was named {{ill|Hōei-yama|ja|宝永山|qq=|12=draft}}.
* {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=|12=draft}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1853|ja|1853|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 23|ja|12月23日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ietsuna|ja|徳川家定|qq=|12=draft}}, the 13th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate, assumed office.

== Births ==
* [[寛正]] 6th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1465|ja|1465|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 11|ja|12月11日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshinobu|ja|足利義尚|qq=|12=draft}}, the 9th shōgun of the Ashikaga Shogunate (died {{ill|1489|ja|1489|qq=|12=draft}}).<ref>{{Kotobank|足利義尚|qq=}}</ref>

