== Births == * [[:en:寛正|寛正]] 6th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1465|1465]] [[:en:December 11|December 11]]) – [[:en:Ashikaga Yoshihisa|Ashikaga Yoshinobu]], the 9th shōgun of the Ashikaga Shogunate (died {{ill|1489|ja|1489|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1489|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}).<ref>{{Kotobank|足利義尚|qq=}}</ref>
