{{afc comment|Wikidata entry [[d:Q840512]] Wikidata name: 23rd day of the 11th month in the Chinese calendar [[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 08:37, 11 June 2025 (UTC)}} {{Not to be confused with|November 23|qq=November 23}}[[Category:Days of the Japanese Lunisolar Calendar]]<!--why is this category always showing up as 347 members?--> {{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=十一月廿三|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 11월 23일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar November|qq=}} '''November 23''' is the 23rd day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November (Lunisolar)|qq=}}, the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senbu|qid=Q96759842}}{{efn|ja|先負|1=Rokuyō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q9418169}}{{efn|1=Rokuyō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q9418169}}{{efn|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senbu|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 六曜|1=Rokuyō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q9418169}}.
== Events == * [[:en:暦仁|暦仁]] 1st year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1238|1238]] [[:en:December 30|December 30]]） – Due to extraordinary omens, the era name was changed from [[:en:Katei|嘉禎]] to [[:en:Ryakunin|暦仁]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://example.com|title=Reference needed|accessdate=2021-04|qq=}}</ref> * [[:en:Genroku|Genroku]] 16th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1703|1703]] [[:en:December 31|December 31]]） – The Genroku Great Earthquake occurred. * [[:en:Hōei|Hōei]] 4th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1707|1707]] [[:en:December 16|December 16]]) – Mount Fuji’s great eruption (the Hōei eruption) occurred; a new volcanic cone appeared on its eastern flank and was named [[:en:Mount Hōei|Hōei-yama]]. * [[:en:Kaei|Kaei]] 6th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1853|1853]] [[:en:December 23|December 23]]) – [[:en:Tokugawa Iesada|Tokugawa Ietsuna]], the 13th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate, assumed office.
== Births == * [[:en:寛正|寛正]] 6th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1465|1465]] [[:en:December 11|December 11]]) – [[:en:Ashikaga Yoshihisa|Ashikaga Yoshinobu]], the 9th shōgun of the Ashikaga Shogunate (died [[:en:1489|1489]]).<ref>{{Kotobank|足利義尚|qq=}}</ref>
