'''November 23''' is the 23rd day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November (Lunisolar)|qq=}}, the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senbu|WD=Q96759842|1=senpu}}{{efn|ja|先負|1=Rokuyō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q9418169}}{{efn|1=Rokuyō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q9418169}}{{efn|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senbu|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 六曜|1=Rokuyō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q9418169}}.

== Events ==
* [[:en:暦仁|暦仁]] 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|WD=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1238|en|1238|WD=Q5433|lt=1238|1=1238}} {{ill|December 30|en|December 30|WD=Q2901|lt=December 30|1=December 30}}） – Due to extraordinary omens, the era name was changed from {{ill|Katei|en|Katei|WD=Q651897|lt=嘉禎|1=Katei}} to {{ill|Ryakunin|en|Ryakunin|WD=Q1193948|lt=暦仁|1=Ryakunin}}.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://example.com|title=Reference needed|accessdate=2021-04|qq=}}</ref>
* {{ill|Genroku|en|Genroku|WD=Q1325001|lt=Genroku|1=Genroku}} 16th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1703|en|1703|WD=Q6822|lt=1703|1=1703}} {{ill|December 31|en|December 31|WD=Q2912|lt=December 31|1=December 31}}） – The Genroku Great Earthquake occurred.
* {{ill|Hōei|en|Hōei|WD=Q1145262|lt=Hōei|1=Hōei}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1707|en|1707|WD=Q6841|lt=1707|1=1707}} {{ill|December 16|en|December 16|WD=Q2410|lt=December 16|1=December 16}}) – Mount Fuji’s great eruption (the Hōei eruption) occurred; a new volcanic cone appeared on its eastern flank and was named {{ill|Mount Hōei|en|Mount Hōei|WD=Q19900675|lt=Hōei-yama|1=Mount Hōei}}.
* {{ill|Kaei|en|Kaei|WD=Q1146125|lt=Kaei|1=Kaei}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1853|en|1853|WD=Q7666|lt=1853|1=1853}} {{ill|December 23|en|December 23|WD=Q2676|lt=December 23|1=December 23}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Iesada|en|Tokugawa Iesada|WD=Q336383|lt=Tokugawa Ietsuna|1=Tokugawa Iesada}}, the 13th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate, assumed office.

== Births ==
* [[:en:寛正|寛正]] 6th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|WD=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1465|en|1465|WD=Q6556|lt=1465|1=1465}} {{ill|December 11|en|December 11|WD=Q2363|lt=December 11|1=December 11}}) – {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshihisa|en|Ashikaga Yoshihisa|WD=Q447639|lt=Ashikaga Yoshinobu|1=Ashikaga Yoshihisa}}, the 9th shōgun of the Ashikaga Shogunate (died {{ill|1489|en|1489|WD=Q6665|lt=1489|1=1489}}).<ref>{{Kotobank|足利義尚|qq=}}</ref>

